# Cursor Rules for kintone PL Dashboard Project

## Language Settings
- All commit messages and code comments should be written in Japanese
- Commit message generation should output in Japanese
- Code documentation and comments should be in Japanese

## Commit Message Format
- Use Japanese for all commit messages
- Follow conventional commit format when possible, but in Japanese
- Example: "feat: 新機能を追加" instead of "feat: Add new feature"

## Code Style
- Write code comments in Japanese
- Write JSDoc comments in Japanese
- Variable and function names can be in English, but comments should be in Japanese

## AI Assistant Instructions
- When generating commit messages, always use Japanese
- When explaining code, use Japanese
- When suggesting changes, provide explanations in Japanese

